Package com.jab125.util.forgehelper.util

package com.jab125.util.forgehelper.util
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Constants
     
    Constants.BlockFlags
    The flags used when calling net.minecraft.world.IWorldWriter#setBlockState(BlockPos, BlockState, int)
    Can be found from World#setBlockState(BlockPos, BlockState, int), World#markAndNotifyBlock, and WorldRenderer#notifyBlockUpdate
    Flags can be combined with bitwise OR
    Constants.NBT
    NBT Tag type IDS, used when storing the nbt to disc, Should align with net.minecraft.nbt.INBT#create and net.minecraft.nbt.INBT#getTypeName Main use is checking tag type in net.minecraft.nbt.CompoundNBT#contains(String, int)
    Constants.WorldEvents
    The world event IDS, used when calling IWorld#playEvent(int, BlockPos, int).
